com.b2international.snowowl.dsl.escg

Interface EscgPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    EscgPackage

    public static interface EscgPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
